my blog, realized with hexo.js

Don't forget to checkout nkoehring/hexo-theme, if you try to build the default
blog.

Then you can just do:

```sh
cd hexo-blog
npm install && ./node_modules/.bin/hexo g && ./node_modules/.bin/hexo s
```

